OL,3,CHopsital sandwich link to women's
OL,4,Clisteria deaths, inquest hears
OL,6,FTwo women died after eating hospital
OL,7,Fchicken mayo sandwiches suspected of
OL,8,Fcontaining listeria, an inquest has
OL,9,Fheard.
OL,11,FManchester Coroner's Court heard how
OL,12,Fretired Jamaican nurse Beverley Sowah,
OL,13,F57, and mother-of-five Enid Heap, 84,
OL,14,Fwere given the sandwiches on
OL,15,Fsuccessive days while patients at
OL,16,FManchester Royal Infirmary (MRI) in
OL,17,F2019.
