OL,3,CHopsital sandwich link to women's
OL,4,Clisteria deaths, inquest hears
OL,6,FThe pair, who had underlying ill
OL,7,Fhealth conditions died days later,
OL,8,Fpart of a nationwide alert over the
OL,9,Flisteria outbreak.
OL,11,FThe court heard how the source of the
OL,12,Fbacteria was linked to an external
OL,13,Ffood supplier which was not the
OL,14,Fkitchens at the hospital.
OL,16,FA joint inquest for both women, with a
OL,17,Fjury of five men and two women, began
OL,18,Fon 11 March, scheduled to last five
OL,19,Fdays, with loved ones of both Mrs
OL,20,FSowah and Mrs Heap attending.
