OL,3,CHopsital sandwich link to women's
OL,4,Clisteria deaths, inquest hears
OL,6,FAlso represented are lawyers for North
OL,7,FCountry Quality Food, based in
OL,8,FSalford, who supplied the chicken to
OL,9,Fthe Good Food Chain.
OL,11,FGood Food Chain made the sandwiches
OL,12,Ffrom their "Whole lotta Good" range,
OL,13,Fsupplied to hospitals, via a contract
OL,14,Fwith Sodexo.
OL,16,FBoth the meat supplier and sandwich
OL,17,Fmaker firms have since gone into
OL,18,Fliquidation.
