OL,3,CHopsital sandwich link to women's
OL,4,Clisteria deaths, inquest hears
OL,6,FThe Good Food Chain, based in Stone,
OL,7,FStaffordshire, made up to 40,000
OL,8,Fsandwiches a day, supplying around 70
OL,9,Fhospitals.
OL,11,FListeria can cause an illness called
OL,12,Flisteriosis, which can be fatal for
OL,13,Fpeople with weakened immune systems.
OL,15,FIn opening remarks at the start of the
OL,16,Fhearing, Zak Golombeck, Manchester
OL,17,Fcity coroner, said: "This case
OL,18,Fconcerns the deaths of two
OL,19,Findividuals, for whom, there is reason
OL,20,Fto suspect, they died of a notifiable
OL,21,Fdisease, namely listeria."
