OL,3,CHopsital sandwich link to women's
OL,4,Clisteria deaths, inquest hears
OL,6,FJamaican-born Mrs Sowah was admitted
OL,7,Fto Manchester Royal Infirmary (MRI) on
OL,8,F15 April 2019, at the time she was
OL,9,Fsuffering from advanced breast cancer.
OL,11,FTwo days later she was given the
OL,12,Fchicken mayo sandwich and died on 26
OL,13,FApril.
OL,15,FThere was no evidence of "sub-optimal"
OL,16,Fcare for Ms Sowah apart from the
OL,17,F"hospital-acquired" listeria infection.
