OL,3,CHopsital sandwich link to women's
OL,4,Clisteria deaths, inquest hears
OL,6,FMrs Heap, a retired chemist shop
OL,7,Fassistant, was admitted to the MRI on
OL,8,FMarch 25 2019 and was served the same
OL,9,Ftype of sandwich on 18 April. She died
OL,10,Fnearly three weeks later on 6 May.
OL,12,FMr Golombeck said the "primary
OL,13,Fhypothesis" was the source of the
OL,14,Flisteria infection was the chicken
OL,15,Fsandwiches consumed by both women.
OL,17,FThe hearing was told the Manchester
OL,18,Flisteria outbreak had the same genetic
OL,19,Flink as another outbreak in Liverpool.
