OL,3,CHopsital sandwich link to women's
OL,4,Clisteria deaths, inquest hears
OL,6,FDr Kirsty Dodgson, consultant
OL,7,Fmicrobiologist at the Manchester
OL,8,FUniversity NHS Foundation Trust, which
OL,9,Fruns the MRI, said in a statement a
OL,10,Fnumber of outbreak meetings were held
OL,11,Fto identify the source of the listeria
OL,12,Fand the Health and Safety Executive
OL,13,Fand Public Health England became
OL,14,Finvolved.
OL,16,FShe said it became a nationwide
OL,17,Finvestigation due to other listeria
OL,18,Fcases in other locations across the
OL,19,Fcountry.
